```plantuml
@startuml miztiik_aws-real-time-use-cases

actor User
participant "GitHub Repository" as Repo
participant "AWS Services" as AWS
participant "External Resources" as ExtRes

User -> Repo: Browse Use Cases
Repo -> User: Display Categorized Use Cases (100-500)
User -> Repo: Select Use Case
Repo -> User: Show Problem Statement & Solution
User -> AWS: Deploy Solution (via provided links/instructions)
AWS -> User: Confirm Deployment/Execution
User -> ExtRes: Access Linked Resources (Docs/Courses)
ExtRes -> User: Provide Additional Learning

@enduml
```